The Cool Access Tier is optimized for data that is accessed infrequently but still requires quick access when needed.

Characteristics:

* Lower storage cost than Hot
* Higher access cost
* Minimum retention period (usually 30 days)

For example, monthly reports stored for occasional review.

A real-life use case is backup files accessed only during recovery.

Another example is logs that are reviewed occasionally.

Cool tier balances cost and accessibility.
